Detailed Description

Definition of the PIP custom header that can be prepended to a packet by external hardware.

Field Documentation

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::grp

POW input group for this packet.

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::grpext

These bits get concatenated with the PKT_INST_HDR[GRP] bits, creating a 6-bit GRP field.

Added in pass2.

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::ngrp

Must be 0 when PKT_INST_HDR[R] = 0.

When set to 1, NGPR prevents PIP from directly using PKT_INST_HDR[GPR] for the GPR value in WQE. When PIP_GBL_CTL[IHMSK_DIS] = 1, Octeon2 does not use NGRP

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::nqos

Must be 0 when PKT_INST_HDR[R] = 0.

When set to 1, NQOS prevents PIP from directly using PKT_INST_HDR[QOS] for the QOS value in WQE. When PIP_GBL_CTL[IHMSK_DIS] = 1, Octeon2 does not use NQOS

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::ntag

Must be 0 when PKT_INST_HDR[R] = 0.

When set to 1, NTAG prevents PIP from directly using PKT_INST_HDR[TAG] for the TAG value in WQE. When PIP_GBL_CTL[IHMSK_DIS] = 1, Octeon2 does not use NTAG

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::ntt

Must be 0 when PKT_INST_HDR[R] = 0.

When set to 1, NTT prevents PIP from directly using PKT_INST_HDR[TT] for the TT value in WQE. When PIP_GBL_CTL[IHMSK_DIS] = 1, Octeon2 does not use NTT

cvmx_pip_port_parse_mode_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::parse_mode

PIP parse mode for this packet.

POW input queue for this packet.

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::rawfull

Documented as R - Set if the Packet is RAWFULL.

If set, this header must be the full 8 bytes

uint64_t cvmx_pip_pkt_inst_hdr_t::reserved0
